{"tid":28371,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"【認真救教】點樣同蠢人相處😂","createTime":"2016-12-08T01:48:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T01:46:55.000Z","uid":13251,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3056195415d5fa2dc586b8c7b53c31dabd9e3035","tid":28371,"uid":13251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T01:48:51.000Z","msg":"父母無受過高等教育就算<br />\n唔講道理、政治等就無問題<br />\n閒話家常<br />\n<br />\n但返工同事好蠢<br />\n咩都問為甚麼 唔識用腦思考<br />\n相處得好累<br />\n老細交間鋪俾我睇 話我話頭醒尾<br />\n但我發覺好多人唔醒目都算<br />\n仲豬咁蠢 教佢地又唔聽<br />\n<br />\n除左耐心 扮傻 仲可以點面對佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c9df299e370fa782f273b4a42a7cc990557894","tid":28371,"uid":37670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T01:50:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>父母無受過高等教育就算<br />\n<br />\n唔講道理、政治等就無問題<br />\n<br />\n閒話家常<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但返工同事好蠢<br />\n<br />\n咩都問為甚麼 唔識用腦思考<br />\n<br />\n相處得好累<br />\n<br />\n老細交間鋪俾我睇 話我話頭醒尾<br />\n<br />\n但我發覺好多人唔醒目都算<br />\n<br />\n仲豬咁蠢 教佢地又唔聽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除左耐心 扮傻 仲可以點面對佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果你唔可以好有耐性咁教一個蠢人,<br />\n其實你同蠢人都無分別, <br />\n只不過你地係蠢係唔同地方"},{"pid":"ee4f07d5332c62dfe09e539d7e96b129fddbf246","tid":28371,"uid":8042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T01:50:36.000Z","msg":"EQ EQ 同埋 EQ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d5fde4c7f513fdbce725fcae168bd374f81f795","tid":28371,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T01:51:19.000Z","msg":"對唔住囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10d7e20fc0d5fc230e04a89a604fdf2d2d57c95b","tid":28371,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T01:51:29.000Z","msg":"你要佢都認同你聰明先聽你講架"},{"pid":"ff8d8ffa11275afadc5d68bbaadf15d9e45d568a","tid":28371,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T01:51:35.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"2791a4b3ca4bd68e4145459b75c7f52442116896","tid":28371,"uid":13251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T01:56:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]<br />\n如果你唔可以好有耐性咁教一個蠢人,<br />\n其實你同蠢人都無分別, <br />\n只不過你地係蠢係唔同地方[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n有道理<br />\n同d蠢人計較只會顯出我既無知同不足<br />\n教唔識佢地就唔好懶叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cf3d8a42ab471e80958081f27ca5e567828ca9b","tid":28371,"uid":13251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T01:57:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>EQ EQ 同埋 EQ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\neq極高啦 打機練返黎<br />\n而家好識做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd208ed0807820c30142a0eb50b57235e478c67f","tid":28371,"uid":13251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T01:59:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你要佢都認同你聰明先聽你講架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實間鋪我入左股算小股東黎<br />\n但佢地唔知 只當我店長 成日當我講既耳邊風<br />\n又唔想用老細身份壓佢地<br />\n講度呢度好似變左關於管理問題<br />\n<br />\n只係想睇下巴絲打點同蠢人相處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff8384608160b8b756506b0195becbdde33ec3e","tid":28371,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:00:37.000Z","msg":"所以好多人以為管理即係有權乜都話哂事，其實MANAGEMENT真係有技巧。<br />\n<br />\n有心學可以上網望下，其實好多入門野睇下就明，跟住試下用下，應該好快上手識管佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c8bca7a603190d748278593b9fe9b7d213f3c46","tid":28371,"uid":13251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:05:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以好多人以為管理即係有權乜都話哂事，其實MANAGEMENT真係有技巧。<br />\n<br />\n有心學可以上網望下，其實好多入門野睇下就明，跟住試下用下，應該好快上手識管佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打我岩岩做管理層<br />\n而家學緊管理方面既知識<br />\n波特定律有無聽過<br />\n<br />\n　　當遭受許多批評時，下級往往只記住開頭的一些，其餘就不聽了，因為他們忙於思索論據來反駁開頭的批評。<br />\n<br />\n　　提出者：英國行為學家L&middot;W&middot;波特<br />\n<br />\n　　點評：總盯著下屬的失誤，是一個領導者的最大失誤。<br />\n<br />\n唯有只睇佢地優點唔着眼缺點<br />\n世界上無蠢人就唔會顯得你聰明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c766b026c41529f2231bd818c0b1eae70c8c8c","tid":28371,"uid":37670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:05:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你要佢都認同你聰明先聽你講架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實間鋪我入左股算小股東黎<br />\n<br />\n但佢地唔知 只當我店長 成日當我講既耳邊風<br />\n<br />\n又唔想用老細身份壓佢地<br />\n<br />\n講度呢度好似變左關於管理問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只係想睇下巴絲打點同蠢人相處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n首先你要埋堆先囉<br />\n你要知道佢地鐘意講D乜<br />\n其實不外乎飲飲食食去旅行"},{"pid":"03c8e341854bb600b9f500834b667ce07ea5242b","tid":28371,"uid":15872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:10:54.000Z","msg":"我都想知<br />\n聽到人問on9問題就開始燥"},{"pid":"da54766db8226e78d219a38dc070b2198b8628c3","tid":28371,"uid":13251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:13:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你要佢都認同你聰明先聽你講架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實間鋪我入左股算小股東黎<br />\n<br />\n但佢地唔知 只當我店長 成日當我講既耳邊風<br />\n<br />\n又唔想用老細身份壓佢地<br />\n<br />\n講度呢度好似變左關於管理問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只係想睇下巴絲打點同蠢人相處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n首先你要埋堆先囉<br />\n你要知道佢地鐘意講D乜<br />\n其實不外乎飲飲食食去旅行</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n埋唔到堆<br />\n其實係唔想埋 因為3個都係台妹崇韓<br />\n而我俾韓國人剝削過 好憎韓國<br />\n佢地就成日講韓劇聽kpop<br />\n食又成日芝士泡菜<br />\n食過一次部隊鍋就唔想再痴佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f960a3440c45d6fb68bbdc97cb16e1bda7521c","tid":28371,"uid":13251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T04:39:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想知<br />\n聽到人問on9問題就開始燥</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n&quot;相處&quot;真係一門學問黎<br />\n教蠢人仲要因材施教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f1229b36014635b28dd4b4e2ad5cfc4ee4a07a","tid":28371,"uid":37979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:05:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>父母無受過高等教育就算<br />\n唔講道理、政治等就無問題<br />\n閒話家常<br />\n<br />\n但返工同事好蠢<br />\n咩都問為甚麼 唔識用腦思考<br />\n相處得好累<br />\n老細交間鋪俾我睇 話我話頭醒尾<br />\n但我發覺好多人唔醒目都算<br />\n仲豬咁蠢 教佢地又唔聽<br />\n<br />\n除左耐心 扮傻 仲可以點面對佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食狗不理包子"},{"pid":"085e13f491db8131f3850d4d56f7c83271564c28","tid":28371,"uid":53438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:44:59.000Z","msg":"呢個世界個個醒你就冇value <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fab1287659bd518ae870cefc12e3dd728519164","tid":28371,"uid":48947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:46:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你要佢都認同你聰明先聽你講架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實間鋪我入左股算小股東黎<br />\n但佢地唔知 只當我店長 成日當我講既耳邊風<br />\n又唔想用老細身份壓佢地<br />\n講度呢度好似變左關於管理問題<br />\n<br />\n只係想睇下巴絲打點同蠢人相處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n蠢唔係最大問題，蠢但係又成日認叻唔肯聽人講先最仆街"},{"pid":"0b33f15081f970086526a852307263d0d92b004a","tid":28371,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:49:35.000Z","msg":"個個都聰明嘅話，仲會有人同你打工咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef7855a60abb8e3511c94d35fc6abbea10e9bb9a","tid":28371,"uid":13251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:13:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個世界個個醒你就冇value <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都明呢點<br />\n可唔可以講下點同佢地相處啊<br />\n求教相處之道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ed783b473136a5921611b23d0b70ac2a481dbf","tid":28371,"uid":13251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:16:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只係想睇下巴絲打點同蠢人相處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n蠢唔係最大問題，蠢但係又成日認叻唔肯聽人講先最仆街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係啊 唔識分莊閒 唔識知己知彼<br />\n明明做錯又死要面唔認錯<br />\n呢d人都唔識做人 我人際關係好都唔識點同佢地相處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3371a1ade7d10d2c4407bf359d8495c0bc3dad2c","tid":28371,"uid":13251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:18:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個個都聰明嘅話，仲會有人同你打工咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都知如果佢地夠聰明可能已經往上爬<br />\n踩住我叫我聽佢支笛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁即係點同佢地呢類人相處啊巴打"},{"pid":"9b5c5041d5ea43ff1a702c1c62fa5cadeaabe70c","tid":28371,"uid":38047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:19:54.000Z","msg":"咁我又覺得蠢都好啲，起碼你心裡面都有個底。<br />\n但係懶就真係冇撚得救，真係會激鳩死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d3636f68d28a6cf2179ec051120359f812647f","tid":28371,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:24:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個個都聰明嘅話，仲會有人同你打工咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都知如果佢地夠聰明可能已經往上爬<br />\n踩住我叫我聽佢支笛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁即係點同佢地呢類人相處啊巴打</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實個個人都應該有優點有長處<br />\n如果你一直都睇唔到嘅話，一係你觀察力有問題，一係你請錯人"},{"pid":"4c3931878098c9185afa2cb161202994b1f03f61","tid":28371,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:25:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>個個都聰明嘅話，仲會有人同你打工咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都知如果佢地夠聰明可能已經往上爬<br />\n踩住我叫我聽佢支笛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁即係點同佢地呢類人相處啊巴打</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實個個人都應該有優點有長處<br />\n如果你一直都睇唔到嘅話，一係你觀察力有問題，一係你請錯人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n補充返先：<br />\n相處主要係待人以寛<br />\n唔好期望每個人仆心仆命或者聰明絕頂<br />\n個人寛容啲，自己都開心啲"}]}